{"id":948,"parent_id":946,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":948,"title":"Haggai 2","subtitle":"","short_title":"Hag.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 2"],[".studySummary",["i","Haggai speaks about the Messiah—The Desire of All Nations will come—The Lord will give peace in His temple."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.1","order":"02.38.002.62669"},["b","1"],"In the seventh",["i",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"month"],","],"in the one and twentieth",["i","day"],"of the month, came the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"by the prophet Haggai, saying,"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.2","order":"02.38.002.62670"},["b","2"],"Speak now to Zerubbabel the son of Shealtiel, governor of Judah, and to Joshua the son of Josedech, the high priest, and to the residue of the people, saying,"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.3","order":"02.38.002.62671"},["b","3"],"Who",["i","is"],"left among you that saw this",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"house"],"in her first glory? and how do ye see it now?",["i","is it"],"not in your eyes in comparison of it as nothing?"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.4","order":"02.38.002.62672"},["b","4"],"Yet now be strong, O Zerubbabel, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; and be strong, O Joshua, son of Josedech, the high priest; and be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"strong"],", all ye people of the land, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and work: for I",["i","am"],"with you, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts:"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.5","order":"02.38.002.62673"},["b","5"],["i","According to"],"the word that I covenanted with you when ye came out of Egypt, so my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"spirit"],"remaineth among you: fear ye not."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.6","order":"02.38.002.62674"},["b","6"],"For thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts; Yet once, it",["i","is"],"a little while, and I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"shake"],"the heavens, and the earth, and the sea, and the dry",["i","land;"]],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.7","order":"02.38.002.62675"},["b","7"],"And I will shake all nations, and the desire of all nations shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"come"],": and I will fill this house with",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"glory"],", saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.8","order":"02.38.002.62676"},["b","8"],"The",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"silver"],["i","is"],"mine, and the gold",["i","is"],"mine, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.9","order":"02.38.002.62677"},["b","9"],"The glory of this latter house shall be greater than of the former, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts: and in this place will I give",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"peace"],", saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.10","order":"02.38.002.62678"},["b","10"],"¶In the four and twentieth",["i","day"],"of the ninth",["i",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"month"],","],"in the second year of Darius, came the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"by Haggai the prophet, saying,"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.11","order":"02.38.002.62679"},["b","11"],"Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts; Ask now the priests",["i","concerning"],"the law, saying,"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.12","order":"02.38.002.62680"},["b","12"],"If one bear holy flesh in the skirt of his garment, and with his skirt do touch bread, or pottage, or wine, or oil, or any meat, shall it be holy? And the priests answered and said, No."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.13","order":"02.38.002.62681"},["b","13"],"Then said Haggai, If",["i","one that is"],"unclean by a dead body touch any of these, shall it be unclean? And the priests answered and said, It shall be unclean."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.14","order":"02.38.002.62682"},["b","14"],"Then answered Haggai, and said, So",["i","is"],"this people, and so",["i","is"],"this nation before me, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; and so",["i","is"],"every work of their hands; and that which they offer there",["i","is"],"unclean."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.15","order":"02.38.002.62683"},["b","15"],"And now, I pray you, consider from this day and upward, from before a stone was laid upon a stone in the temple of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],":"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.16","order":"02.38.002.62684"},["b","16"],"Since those",["i","days"],"were, when",["i","one"],"came to an heap of twenty",["i","measures,"],"there were",["i","but"],"ten: when",["i","one"],"came to the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"pressfat"],"for to draw out fifty",["i","vessels"],"out of the press, there were",["i","but"],"twenty."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.17","order":"02.38.002.62685"},["b","17"],"I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"smote"],"you with",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"blasting"],"and with mildew and with hail in all the labours of your hands; yet ye",["i",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_17c"},"turned"]],"not to me, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.18","order":"02.38.002.62686"},["b","18"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"Consider"],"now from this day and upward, from the four and twentieth day of the ninth",["i","month, even"],"from the day that the foundation of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"’s temple was laid, consider",["i","it."]],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.19","order":"02.38.002.62687"},["b","19"],"Is the seed yet in the barn? yea, as yet the vine, and the fig tree, and the pomegranate, and the olive tree, hath not brought forth: from this day will I bless",["i","you."]],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.20","order":"02.38.002.62688"},["b","20"],"¶And again the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"came unto Haggai in the four and twentieth",["i","day"],"of the month, saying,"],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.21","order":"02.38.002.62689"},["b","21"],"Speak to Zerubbabel, governor of Judah, saying, I will shake the heavens and the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"earth"],";"],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.22","order":"02.38.002.62690"},["b","22"],"And I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"overthrow"],"the throne of kingdoms, and I will destroy the strength of the kingdoms of the heathen; and I will overthrow the chariots, and those that ride in them; and the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_22b"},"horses"],"and their riders shall come down, every one by the sword of his",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_22c"},"brother"],"."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.23","order":"02.38.002.62691"},["b","23"],"In that day, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts, will I take thee, O Zerubbabel, my servant, the son of Shealtiel, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and will make thee as",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"a signet"],": for I have",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_23b"},"chosen"],"thee, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.1a","order":"02.38.002.62692"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hag/1.1"},"Hag. 1:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.3a","order":"02.38.002.62694"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezra/3.12.11-13"},"Ezra 3:12 (11–13)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.4a","order":"02.38.002.62696"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.15.15-18"},"D&C 27:15 (15–18)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/75.22"},"75:22"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.5a","order":"02.38.002.62698"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/29.45.41,45"},"Ex. 29:45 (41, 45)"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.6a","order":"02.38.002.62700"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/13.13"},"Isa. 13:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/38.19.19-20"},"Ezek. 38:19 (19–20)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/last-days"},"TG Last Days"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.7a","order":"02.38.002.62702"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-second-coming"},"TG Jesus Christ, Second Coming"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.7b","order":"02.38.002.62704"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/40.34"},"Ex. 40:34"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/60.7"},"Isa. 60:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/97.15"},"D&C 97:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.8a","order":"02.38.002.62706"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.39"},"D&C 38:39"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.9a","order":"02.38.002.62708"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/peace"},"TG Peace"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/peace-of-god"},"Peace of God"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.10a","order":"02.38.002.62710"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hag/1.1"},"Hag. 1:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.16a","order":"02.38.002.62712"},["b","16a"],["span.small","IE"],"winevat."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.17a","order":"02.38.002.62714"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/28.22"},"Deut. 28:22"],"."],["div",{"id":"17b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.17b","order":"02.38.002.62716"},["b","17b"],["span.small","IE"],"rust, smut, or blight."],["div",{"id":"17c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.17c","order":"02.38.002.62718"},["b","17c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.3"},"Jer. 5:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/4.6.6-11"},"Amos 4:6 (6–11)"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.18a","order":"02.38.002.62720"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hag/1.5"},"Hag. 1:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.21a","order":"02.38.002.62722"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/earth-destiny-of"},"TG Earth, Destiny of"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.22a","order":"02.38.002.62724"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/2.44"},"Dan. 2:44"],"."],["div",{"id":"22b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.22b","order":"02.38.002.62726"},["b","22b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/micah/5.10"},"Micah 5:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"22c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.22c","order":"02.38.002.62728"},["b","22c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zech/14.13"},"Zech. 14:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.23a","order":"02.38.002.62730"},["b","23a"],["span.small","IE"],"one having authority."],["div",{"id":"23b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.23b","order":"02.38.002.62732"},["b","23b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/89.3"},"Ps. 89:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/43.10"},"Isa. 43:10"],"."]]}
